<FONT SIZE="1" FACE="verdana, arial"><B>Updated:</B> August 13th 2000</FONT><BR><BR>
<FONT SIZE="1" COLOR="#FF0000" FACE="ariel"><B>Unfinished</B></FONT><BR><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="verdana, arial">

Speak with Magi Frinon, Frederic Calermin and Roanis Elindar for these Magician specific quests...<BR><BR>

<B>Clarification:</B> This results in a Bracelet of Clarification [AC 6.  +1 char, +9 int, +10 mana].  You need a Crimson tessera, Ethereal Sapphire and a Feathered Cape.<BR><BR>

<B>Empowerment:</B> This results in a <A HREF="armor_detail.php3?search=848">Mask of Empowerment</A>.  You need an Iron Disk, a Gem of Empowerment and a Ceramic Mask.<BR><BR>

<B>Shielding:</B>  This Results in a Golden White Pendant.  You need a Hyaline Globe, Ivory Pendant and a Gold Coffer.<BR><BR>

<B>Interpretation:</B> This results in a Duennan Shielding Ring.  You need a Carmine Spiroc Feather, Blood Sky Amethyst and a Golden Efreeti Ring.<BR><BR>

<B>Displacement:</B>  This results in a Staff of Elemental Mastery.  You need some Sweet Nectar, a Crown of Elemental Mastery, a Large Opal and a Djinni's Stave.<BR><BR>

<B>Summoning:</B> This results in a Drake Hide Amice.  You need a harpy Statuette, Finely Woven Cloth Amice and a Big Diamond.<BR><BR>

<B>Gesticulation:</B>  Reward unknown.  You need an Efreeti Magi Staff, Sweet Nectar, a Sphinx Crown and a Hazy Opal.<BR><BR>



